<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<base target="_top">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{$basePath}/css/loader.css">
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Condensed:400,700&amp;subset=latin,latin-ext" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha512-dTfge/zgoMYpP7QbHy4gWMEGsbsdZeCXz7irItjcC3sPUFtf0kuFbDz/ixG7ArTxmDjLXDmezHubeNikyKGVyQ==" crossorigin="anonymous">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css" integrity="sha384-aUGj/X2zp5rLCbBxumKTCw2Z50WgIr1vs/PFN4praOTvYXWlVyh2UtNUU0KAUhAX" crossorigin="anonymous">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{$basePath}/css/main.css">
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.0/jquery.min.js" defer></script>
		<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha512-K1qjQ+NcF2TYO/eI3M6v8EiNYZfA95pQumfvcVrTHtwQVDG+aHRqLi/ETn2uB+1JqwYqVG3LIvdm9lj6imS/pQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" defer></script>
		<script src="{$basePath}/js/main.js" defer></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="page">
			<h1>Cortis mailbox</h1>
			<div id="content">
				<div id="select-command-panel" class="menu-panel hidden">
				</div>
				<div class="loader" id="loader">
				</div>
				<div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert" style="display:none;">
				</div>
				<div class="ls-panel content-panel" id="ls-panel">
					<h2>Výpis emailů</h2>
					<p>Zašlete e-mail na adresu <a href="mailto:cortis@ion.cz">cortis@ion.cz</a> a měl by se do několika sekund objevit zde:</p>
					<div id="ls-content">
						<table class="table table-striped">'
							<tr>
								<th>Odesílatel</th>
								<th>Subject</th>
								<th>Datum</th>
								<th>Text</th>
							</tr>
							{foreach $emails as $email}
								<tr>
									<td>{$email->from}</td>
									<td>{$email->subject|truncate:40}</td>
									<td>{$email->date}</td>
									<td>{$email->body_text|truncate:50}</td>
								</tr>
							{/foreach}
						</table>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<footer>Jakub Bouček 2017 - only for white-hat hacking!</footer>
	</body>
</html>